contentrichtext.text: {{Italic title prefixed|3}} {{For|a ship with a similar name|USS Norfolk Packet}} '''USS ''Norfolk''''' may refer to: *{{USS|Norfolk|1798}}, was a brig during the Quasi-War with France *''Norfolk'' (CA-137), was a planned [[heavy cruiser]] laid down in December 1944 at the Philadelphia Naval Shipyard, but construction was canceled in August 1945. *{{USS|Norfolk|DL-1}}, was a destroyer leader in service from 1953 to 1970 *{{USS|Norfolk|SSN-714}}, is a {{sclass|Los Angeles|submarine}} commissioned in 1983 and currently on active service {{Shipindex}} {{DEFAULTSORT:Norfolk}} [[Category:United States Navy ship names]]
